              "id": "l2-3-read",
              "type": "read",
              "title": "Read Genesis 2:7–25",
              "ref": "Genesis 2:7-25",
              "reflectPrompt": "How does God's care in shaping Adam and Eve contrast with the broad strokes of Genesis 1?"
